---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Dyspnoea — Breathlessness and the Heart — Dr Delhasse" description="Breathlessness can have a cardiac origin. Discover when dyspnoea requires a cardiology consultation." lang="en">

  <section class="hero-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1><span class="text-primary">Dyspnoea</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">When breathlessness comes from the heart</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container detail-content">
      <img src="/images/svg/symptomes/Disnea.svg" alt="Dyspnoea" class="detail-icon" />

      <p>If you experience breathlessness without an obvious reason, such as without having exerted yourself, it is common to assume it comes from the lungs. Yet the possible causes are numerous, and the origin may be hidden. When the problem is mild, one sometimes chooses to live with it without consulting. This happens particularly in elderly people, whose reduced mobility delays the onset of symptoms.</p>

      <p>In these situations, abnormal breathlessness can go unnoticed, delaying investigations or treatment. It is often only when the problem worsens to the point of becoming an emergency that the cause is identified.</p>

      <p>The heart — responsible for circulating blood throughout the body — may be involved. Its function can be impaired by a weakened muscle, damaged valves or rhythm disorders, leading to heart failure. This condition frequently manifests as a sensation of breathlessness, even during minimal activities.</p>

      <p>Consulting your doctor allows early detection of these problems, improvement of your symptoms and protection of your long-term health.</p>

      <div class="detail-cta">
        <a href="/en/symptoms" class="btn btn--outline">&larr; All symptoms</a>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book an appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-page { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, #1a3d6d 100%); padding: 6rem 0 4rem; color: var(--color-white); }
  .hero-page h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: 2.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .detail-content { max-width: 800px; }
  .detail-icon { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-content p { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-gray); }
  .detail-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
</style>
